                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9696" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1456</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1036 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“分拆”风云起，上市正当时？——曙光数创上市之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The &quot;Spin-off&quot; Trend is Surging，Is It the Right Time for Listing? —— The Listing Journey of Shuguang Digital Technology Co., Ltd.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑鹏，苏美娟，郑鑫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曙光数据基础设施创新技术（北京）股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">分拆上市；中科曙光；曙光数创</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">spin-off and listing, Zhongke Dawn, Dawn Digital Creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，许多大型企业面对业务过度多元的情况，感到力不从心。分拆上市作为资产重组和资源优化的一种方式，能够有效加强业务核心化，加强公司的核心竞争力。自2019年中国证监会发布《上市公司分拆所属子公司境内上市试点若干规定》以来，A股市场就掀起了分拆上市的热潮。本案例以2022年11月18日曙光数创成功分拆上市为例，重点介绍中科曙光分拆曙光数创上市的背景、动因、过程、路径和效果，旨在引导学生深入理解分拆上市的含义，探究分拆上市的动因，熟悉不同的分拆路径，思考分拆上市对企业发展带来的影响，进而提升学生对企业分拆上市行为的分析和判断能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, many large enterprises have been exhausted in the face of excessive business diversification. As a way of asset restructuring and resource optimization, spin-off and listing can effectively strengthen the coreization of the business and strengthen the core competitiveness of the company. Since the Securities Regulatory Commission issued the spin-off rules in 2019, more and more enterprises have chosen to take the road of spin-off and listing. This case takes the successful spin-off and listing of Shuguang Digital Creation on November 18, 2022 as an example, focusing on the background, motives, process, path and effect of Zhongke Shuguang&#39;s spin-off and listing of Shuguang Digital Creation. The case is designed to help students thoroughly grasp the concept of spin-off and listing, deeply consider the reasons behind such actions, comprehend the distinct features of various spin-off methods, investigate the effects of spin-off and listing on corporate development, and thereby enhance their analytical and judgment skills regarding corporate spin-off and listing behaviors.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">分拆上市含义与类型；信息不对称理论；融资需求理论；归核化战略理论；管理层激励理论；事件研究法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-07</td>
                            </tr>
